","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSSuggestionChip","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This provider should be integrated as a ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllChipComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" implementation inside ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" so as to provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" implementation to use.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Custom themes can use subclass of ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" and apply the provider they need.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It implements also the protocol ","type":"text"},{"code":"ChipComponentTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" so as to expose the component tokens for ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"chip"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" through any ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Chip"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of colors (from ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":") ,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"spaces (from ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"), dimensions (","type":"text"},{"code":"AllDimensionSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":")","type":"text"},{"text